ve fun with her! :3</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e1021f4b86f57bb2b99b45705004bb2/c7c04ea2993725db-24/s640x960/3eae07fe621b47c0ee722bb402d5759693a0dbb3.pnj\" alt=\"image\" style=\"width: 923px;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"colo","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"8e04ff78-ed7e-41f7-9f13-d529de001269_f54fe983-3bc4-43b8-a440-c039defe26ee.webp","creator":"Rikup","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🧛 Vampire","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":21113,"messages":338820,"created_at":"2024-11-28T22:03:18.932123+00:00"}